    <title>论系</title>
    <link href="https://tynfms.github.io/2021/02/14/corbuilds/"/>
    <id>https://tynfms.github.io/2021/02/14/corbuilds/</id>
    <published>2021-02-14T02:04:57.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-07-12T08:57:57.886Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>系内运算经典<br><a id="more"></a></p><h3 id="0x01-一个点关于任意直线的对称点"><a href="#0x01-一个点关于任意直线的对称点" class="headerlink" title="0x01.一个点关于任意直线的对称点"></a>0x01.一个点关于任意直线的对称点</h3><p>$P’$为$P({x_0},{y_0})$关于直线$l:Ax+By+C=0$的对称点。<br><a href="https://imgtu.com/i/Wi3M3F"><img src="https://z3.ax1x.com/2021/07/12/Wi3M3F.jpg" alt="Wi3M3F.jpg"></a><br>图中$AB$所在直线即为 $l$。<br>由$AB\bot PP’$可得$k_{PP’} \cdot k_{AB}=-1$，那么 </p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">k_{PP'}=-{1\over{k_{AB} } }=-{1\over{-{B\over{A} } } }={\frac{A}{B} }</script><p>又直线经过 $P$ 点，有 $PP’:y={B\over{A}}(x-{x_0})+{y_0}$，又有 $H$ 为直线 $PP’$ 与 $AB$ 的交点，故</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">H({ {B^2{x_0}-AB{y_0}-AC}\over{A^2+B^2} },{ \frac{A^2{y_0}-AB{x_0}-BC}{A^2+B^2} })</script><p>又根据$H$为$P,P’$两点的中点，可以推算出，</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">P'({ {(B^2-A^2){x_0}-2AB{y_0}-2AC}\over{A^2+B^2} },{ {(A^2-B^2){y_0}-2AB{x_0}-2BC}\over{A^2+B^2} })</script><h3 id="0x02-一条直线关于任意直线的对称直线"><a href="#0x02-一条直线关于任意直线的对称直线" class="headerlink" title="0x02.一条直线关于任意直线的对称直线"></a>0x02.一条直线关于任意直线的对称直线</h3><p>$l’$为$l:Lx+My+N=0$关于直线$l_0:Ax+By+C=0$的对称直线。<br><a href="https://imgtu.com/i/WC8yxH"><img src="https://z3.ax1x.com/2021/07/11/WC8yxH.jpg" alt="WC8yxH.jpg"></a><br>我们作出$l$与$y,x$轴的交点$A,B$，作两点关于$l_0$的对称点$A’,B’$，根据$0x01$中的公式，可以推算出</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">A'(\frac{2ABN-2ACM}{M(A^2+B^2)},\frac{N(B^2-A^2)-2BCM}{M(A^2+B^2)}),B'(\frac{N(A^2-B^2)-2ACL}{L(A^2+B^2)},\frac{2ABN-2BCL}{L(A^2+B^2)})</script><p>那么$l’$便是过$A’,B’$两点的直线，可算出</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">k=\frac{\frac{2ABN-2BCL}{L(A^2+B^2)}-\frac{N(B^2-A^2)-2BCM}{M(A^2+B^2)}}{\frac{N(A^2-B^2)-2ACL}{L(A^2+B^2)}-\frac{2ABN-2ACM}{M(A^2+B^2)}}=\frac{2ABM+L(A^2-B^2)}{-2ABL+M(A^2-B^2)}</script><p>从而</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">b=\frac{N(B^2-A^2)-2BCM}{M(A^2+B^2)}-\frac{2ABM+L(A^2-B^2)}{-2ABL+M(A^2-B^2)} \times \frac{2ABN-2ACM}{M(A^2+B^2)}=\frac{2ACL+2BCM-N(A^2+B^2)}{-2ABL+M(A^2-B^2)}</script><p>推算出$l’$的一般式，</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">l':(2ABM+L(A^2-B^2))x+(2ABL+M(B^2-A^2))y+2ACL+2BCM-N(A^2+B^2)=0</script><h3 id="0x03-三角形的内心坐标公式"><a href="#0x03-三角形的内心坐标公式" class="headerlink" title="0x03.三角形的内心坐标公式"></a>0x03.三角形的内心坐标公式</h3><h4 id="备用芝士：奔驰定理"><a href="#备用芝士：奔驰定理" class="headerlink" title="备用芝士：奔驰定理"></a>备用芝士：奔驰定理</h4><p><a href="https://imgtu.com/i/WiJO8f"><img src="https://z3.ax1x.com/2021/07/12/WiJO8f.jpg" alt="WiJO8f.jpg"></a></p><p>对于$\triangle ABC$内的任意一点$P$，有</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">S_{\triangle PBC} \cdot \overrightarrow{PA} + S_{\triangle PAC} \cdot \overrightarrow{PB} + S_{\triangle PAB} \cdot \overrightarrow{PC} = 0</script><h4 id="正题"><a href="#正题" class="headerlink" title="正题"></a>正题</h4><p><a href="https://imgtu.com/i/WiDSqf"><img src="https://z3.ax1x.com/2021/07/12/WiDSqf.jpg" alt="WiDSqf.jpg"></a><br>由<strong>奔驰定理</strong>，知</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">S_{\triangle IBC} \cdot \overrightarrow{IA} + S_{\triangle IAC} \cdot \overrightarrow{IB} + S_{\triangle IAB} \cdot \overrightarrow{IC} = 0</script><p>因为$I$是内心，所以$H_{A}I = H_{B}I = H_{C}I = h$，故</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\left\{\begin{aligned}S_{\triangle IAB} = \frac{1}{2}AB \cdot IH_{C} = \frac{1}{2}AB \cdot h\\S_{\triangle IBC} = \frac{1}{2}BC \cdot IH_{A} = \frac{1}{2}BC \cdot h\\S_{\triangle IAC} = \frac{1}{2}AC \cdot IH_{B} = \frac{1}{2}AC \cdot h\\\end{aligned}\right.</script><p>以上式子代入得</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">AB \cdot \overrightarrow{IC} + BC \cdot \overrightarrow{IA} + AC \cdot \overrightarrow{IB} = 0</script><p>设$A(x_A,y_A),B(x_B,y_B),C(x_C,y_C),I(x,y),a=BC,b=AC,c=AB$，可知</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\left\{\begin{aligned}\overrightarrow{IA} = (x_A - x, y_A - y) \\\overrightarrow{IB} = (x_B - x, y_B - y) \\\overrightarrow{IC} = (x_C - x, y_C - y) \\\end{aligned}\right.</script><p>代入，可以得到</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\left\{\begin{aligned}a (x_A - x) + b (x_B - x) + c (x_C - x) = 0 \\a (y_A - y) + b (y_B - y) + c (y_C - y) = 0\end{aligned}\right.</script><p>得结论</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">I(\frac{ax_A+bx_B+cx_C}{a+b+c}, \frac{ay_A+by_B+cy_C}{a+b+c})</script>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;系内运算经典&lt;br&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
    
